format: YAML-like configuration/include file for build metadata
description: This file contains build configuration settings and tuning parameters for the ARM Cortex-A65 processor within the Yocto Project build system. It specifies compiler arguments, feature flags, dependencies, and architecture-specific configurations.

methods.name: bb.utils.contains
methods.description: Utility function to check if a specific feature is present in a list or string, used here to conditionally append compiler flags.
